  "runtime_notes": [
    "Command aliases are prompt recipes under commands/ and are not native Codex slash commands.",
    "Workflow agent wording is adapted into inline role-prompt usage unless the user explicitly requests parallel Codex subagents.",
    "Stored journal profiles are estimates until current official or user-provided guidelines are checked in the active task.",
    "Data-derived figure outputs require supplied data or runnable code; missing data outputs must be marked NON_DATA_MOCKUP.",
    "Underspecified figure requests route to fig-scope/intake-design before rendering.",
    "Renderer registry entries must validate before registry-based rendering.",
    "Visual regression audits are render-quality checks, not proof of scientific correctness.",
    "Multi-panel layout audits check optical grid, colorbar spacing, semantic color mapping, and controlled direct labels.",
    "Library pool selection is plan-only and must not install packages automatically.",
    "External data acquisition is plan-only unless the user explicitly approves download with complete provenance."
  ]
